Enum Class InteractionTypeModels

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<InteractionTypeModels>
com.conquest.interactionHandler.InteractionTypeModels
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<InteractionTypeModels>, Constable
public enum InteractionTypeModels extends Enum<InteractionTypeModels>
ðŸ“Œ InteractionTypeModels

Enum representing all supported types of player-to-entity interactions that can trigger a duel challenge based on config.

These values are referenced in challengePlayer.yml under the action-type field. Supported formatting includes:

  • right_click_player
  • SHIFT-RIGHT-CLICK-PLAYER
  • Shift Left Click Player
